(March 5, 1953.)

(Republish.)

The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. John W. Diefendorf, Appellant.

Order unanimously reversed, the proceeding dismissed and the appellant discharged. Settle order on notice. Present — Peek, P. J., Callahan, Breitel, Foster and Bergan, JJ. [See ante, p. 465.]
